<db:abstract>
<db:para>The <db:link xlink:href="qwaylandxdgsurface.xml">QWaylandXdgSurface</db:link> class provides desktop-style compositor-specific features to an xdg surface.</db:para>
<db:para>This class was introduced in Qt 5.12.</db:para>
