<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>This class is part of the <db:link xlink:href="qwaylandxdgshell.xml">QWaylandXdgShell</db:link> extension and provides a way to extend the functionality of an existing <db:link xlink:href="qwaylandsurface.xml">QWaylandSurface</db:link> with features specific to desktop-style compositors, such as resizing and moving the surface.</db:para>
<db:para>It corresponds to the Wayland interface <db:code>xdg_surface</db:code>.</db:para>
</db:section>
